             was indicted for a <rs id="t18220220-62-off336" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18220220-62-off336" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18220220-62-off336" type="offenceSubcategory" value="fraud"></interp>
               fraud
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>MR. BOLLAND conducted the prosecution.</p>
               <p>MR. 
               
                  <persName id="t18220220-62-victim687" type="victimName">
                     JOHN 
                     WATSON
                  <interp inst="t18220220-62-victim687" type="surname" value="WATSON"></interp>
