                  </persName>
               
            . On the 15th of November I was in partnership with 
               
                  <persName id="t18220220-62-victim689" type="victimName">
                     Thomas Osborne 
                     Stock
                  <interp inst="t18220220-62-victim689" type="surname" value="Stock"></interp>
